Class RestInterfaceFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.gsfc.spdf.ssc.RestInterfaceFactory
  • public class RestInterfaceFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a factory for producing objects returned to a client of the Satellite Situation Center REST web services.

      • createDefaultBFieldModel

        public gov.nasa.gsfc.sscweb.schema.BFieldModel createDefaultBFieldModel()
        Creates a default gov.nasa.gsfc.sscweb.schema.BFieldModel object. The default value has an internal model of IGRF, external model of Tsyganenko 89c (KP values of 3-,3,3+), and stop trace altitude of 100 km.
        Returns:
        a default gov.nasa.gsfc.sscweb.schema.BFieldModel object.
